description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Temporary Staffing Bureau is recruiting for several Admin &amp; Clerical positions throughout the Trust.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; We are currently looking for motivated and reliable Administration and Clerical Assistants, to work as part of a growing team. The bank is an ideal way of earning extra money while working on an ad-hoc basis; covering shortages in staffing levels of our permanent staff, or completing short projects. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are currently looking for full-time candidates, able to work Monday - Friday, with various levels of administration and clerical experience who are flexible and reliable with good interpersonal and organisational skills. You will also be computer literate with experience of Word and Excel, and able to maintain the confidentiality required in working in a patient environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Successful candidates will be expected to work across the trust, providing services in a professional, efficient, friendly and polite manner, in line with our values. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; If all of the above sounds appealing and you want to help us further shape our direction of maintaining clinical excellence, then please make an application.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please note, if you are looking for part-time hours, evenings or weekend work we cannot provide this at this current time. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;bankrecruitment@uhbristol.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
